foreignObject.div:
check_circleCompiles circleCI config and
checks that it is up to date

notify_startSends message to IRC
notifying of build start

build_serverRuns gradle bootJar to
build and package (No tests)

release_approvalHolds releases waiting for
manual approval

request_approvalMessages IRC to request
manual approval

notify_successMessages IRC to inform of
successful build and tests

publish_github_releaseTriggers github release and tags
Publishes artifacts to github

docker_releaseBuilds and pushes new
image to docker hub

notify_releaseMessages IRC informing
of new release version
